{"tid":1274703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實發緊夢係唔得閒上連登","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T17:19:22.000Z","uid":164955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa77f5e8816bf07b642f38b1b791038cfbac6530","tid":1274703,"uid":164955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"莫講話連登，手機都唔得閒睇，夢入面個個都有自己崗位，前中後都有，進攻，人鏈運貨，後勤，忙到踢哂腳，收都收得差啦，<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再剩係網上勇武，做網上軍師</span>，真係打緊仗冇人得閒理尻你地㗎。你肯出黎，哪怕你只係細細聲喺牆角聽暗屌林鄭一句，就算剩係捐一枝水出黎(最好唔好企喺橋度食花生)，已經對成個運動好大支持，當然我鼓勵大家可以做多dd。每個人行多一步，成場仗已經好唔同  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏係一齊贏，輸係一撚齊輸㗎<br />\n有個中三同學自己單飛都願意出黎<br />\n你地仲有乜撚嘢藉口唔出呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天佑香港，天佑300</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5880c70927db951e42421bf5cdd498861706532","tid":1274703,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"我真係好愛<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人同年青人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7727db77783d1d28e5ba73da2ae735b64da37f","tid":1274703,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"感謝你地，天佑香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ad8e109961d09c8d869e904474ffa8478ef884","tid":1274703,"uid":164955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"BTW夢醒好肚餓，夢入面剩係食咗午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}